markup_text: Add Accessible bathroom: Provide a circulation space of around 2000 mm x 1600 mm to allow wheelchair turning. Door should swing outward or be sliding so it does not obstruct the circulation area and it should provide a clear opening of at least 850 mm with a flush threshold. Install grab rails around the WC and in the shower, with a fold-down shower seat, and leave at least 800 mm clear space beside the toilet for side transfer. Use slip‑resistant flooring and lever tap fixtures.text
